{"tid":1905233,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人又崩潰了 周子瑜捐5000萬竟被罵爆","createTime":"2020-03-01T06:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T03:50:58.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0df42737fc13db7d4e58977835995be9a3b0f1","tid":1905233,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T06:24:55.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐，韓國疫情慘重，人氣女團「TWICE」台灣成員周子瑜近日就捐出5000萬韓元（約新台幣123萬元）幫助韓國抗疫，令不少民眾相當感動，不過此舉竟意外引來中國網友崩潰狂罵。<br />\n <br />\n據韓媒報導，周子瑜捐出5000萬韓元給「愛心果實」社會福利共同募捐會，這些善款將用於購買醫護人員防護衣、口罩的用品，沒想到此舉就意外登上微博熱搜榜，原來是中國網友又再度崩潰，不滿周子瑜只捐款給韓國，而未捐給中國，但周子瑜粉絲則力挺「愛心不分國界」，雙方大戰因此登上熱搜榜。"},{"pid":"8310d67039ecf7b9f80876812cb285310ce4e1e0","tid":1905233,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa3a67599018dbb1af2e37d9f55d15046a13040","tid":1905233,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T06:28:36.000Z","msg":"唔係又捐返畀支那咩？"},{"pid":"1805b6e5d79284f6b7e5a42003fe85de2ae4d483","tid":1905233,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T06:29:12.000Z","msg":"支那狗落地獄啦"},{"pid":"d5020580202f9c04849ed0126c05f28b07ec85a6","tid":1905233,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"芝麻人咁有錢<br />\n都要人捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519e0b621cd56a5ab1fc2f471d38470c40d9140c","tid":1905233,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"豬乸人話國內疫情已受控，仲捐俾佢益貪官咩?"},{"pid":"526a7f35ab497fc37d041db329e6d994850dd296","tid":1905233,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":